mainText:
Steve Jobs can't be gone... Steve Jobs is an apotheosis, he just can't leave
 the world now. It's not right, he can't be gone! This has to be a nightmare. Steve Jobs has made me who I am today, I just can't bear this. But&nbsp;wherever&nbsp;Steve may be now, at least he has the satisfaction of knowing the entire world will miss him, and how much he affected it. So thank you Steve, wherever you are for all of the good you caused and the technological advancements you've brought that have impacted our way of life and our future. I'm crying
 right now for you  Steve Jobs, you incredible man...&nbsp;
